reviewText: For years I remembered this show visually but couldn't for the life of me remember the name or title of this show. One day Amazon suggested it to me seeing as how I have bought other Anime DVDs & PS3 based games so when I saw this m& started looking it over I was beyond ecstatic to be reminded of it. Soon as I got it in the mail I watched it & it was like a flash back to '95 when I used to watch it as a child. Most definitely worth the buy for your Anime collection.

reviewText: I have liked this series for years. I bought this series because I wanted it on DVD. The only thing I don't like about this set is that it's only in English. I like watching the Japanese version with subtitles as well, and this set didn't have it. Other than that, I'm glad that it had the whole series in one set. Still worth getting.
summary: Glad to see a series set out
